Flashcards v0.3.5

A simple HTML5 app that features:
 * Add / Edit / Delete flashcards through the frontend
 * Uses localStorage to store all of your cards
 * Works offline
 * Separate css for iphone or small screens
 * Detects iphone screen orientation and updates style
 * Point feature for each card to track which cards you need to work more on
 * Randomize feature to study cards in a different order

Try it out at: http://fattarsi.com/m/html5/flashcards/

Recent changes:
 * Style updates for mobile devices
 * Clean up display, uniform button style
 * Default text for first time visitors and after a reset
 * Randomize now creates a new temporary list so prev/next work
 * High/low point filters
 * Some bug fixes